      <title>SEC 针对自己员工的短信行为，禁止在工作电话上使用 WhatsApp</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/sec-targets-its-own-staff-s-texting-nixes-whatsapp-on-agency-s-mobile-phones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会已屏蔽员工工作手机上的第三方消息应用程序和短信，使其自己的做法更接近其为行业执行的标准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/sec-targets-its-own-staff-s-texting-nixes-whatsapp-on-agency-s-mobile-phones</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:01:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大提高资本利得税，为住房筹集数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/canada-hikes-capital-gains-tax-to-raise-billions-for-housing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将提高企业和富人的资本利得税，以帮助支付数百亿美元的新支出，这些支出旨在使住房更加负担得起并帮助年轻人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/canada-hikes-capital-gains-tax-to-raise-billions-for-housing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着纳税额的增加，国库现金余额出现两年来最大增幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/treasury-cash-balance-jumps-most-in-2-years-as-tax-payments-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部的现金余额周一激增，因为政府在四月中旬的所得税截止日期前缴款大量涌入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/treasury-cash-balance-jumps-most-in-2-years-as-tax-payments-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
